{"tid":2225394,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"漫威全新影集《驚奇女士》選角結果出爐 影壇新星挑大樑化身漫威首位穆斯林英雄","createTime":"2020-10-01T09:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T04:54:08.000Z","uid":295230,"like":11,"dislike":81,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"9287da4907ab9a8d853dea6c45a510311acf1c66","tid":2225394,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:45:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gzM4vRm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgzM4vRm.jpg&h=e6672c56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預定將在迪士尼串流平台 Disney+ 獨家開播的漫威女性英雄影集《驚奇女士》（Ms. Marvel）兩週前才宣佈多位導演加入，今日則終於進一步曝光了該劇主人翁「驚奇女士」卡瑪拉克汗的選角結果。外媒《Deadline》獨家披露，初踏好萊塢不久的影壇新人艾蒙薇拉妮（Imon Vellani，上圖左）已被漫威和迪士尼相中，準備演出這部由她首次擔綱主角的作品。<br />\n<br />\n巴基斯坦裔的卡瑪拉克汗，在漫畫中是第四位繼承「驚奇女士」稱號的角色，同時也是漫威宇宙第一位擁有自己個人連載的穆斯林超級英雄。除了登上串流小螢幕，卡瑪拉未來亦會在其它漫威電影中現身。"},{"pid":"4e13beeaedd69b3ade2f9070687b62b3caa031af","tid":2225394,"uid":236891,"like":43,"dislike":2,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"又係女權素食環保人士？"},{"pid":"a4aff0381df14a9e7e9558683d4ee8dbc39db0a6","tid":2225394,"uid":134119,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:24:58.000Z","msg":"係咪變性人？"},{"pid":"3aa88dfc3390928eda66d56227ebf8050281d943","tid":2225394,"uid":125380,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:26:15.000Z","msg":"lesbian?"},{"pid":"2a816e84b075e804c066c643103ac81a2cbc87f9","tid":2225394,"uid":70227,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:26:56.000Z","msg":"經期女士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697edcdc84fe018162e0e430996d8840d34f1558","tid":2225394,"uid":177552,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:27:17.000Z","msg":"打marvel 用呢條女一d代入感都無"},{"pid":"f6a0d8ae19d4c7415465973fca7c06a9519ec43c","tid":2225394,"uid":189150,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T10:28:27.000Z","msg":"認真  其實幾似<img src=\"/